<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
Ok, I got a bit cocky last night (and had dinged 49 with zero xp, so nothing to loose!) <P>Got myself a Medial Telamon, and had a cleric buf him.. (STR/DEX/etc). <P>Pulled a tree with a debuf...RAN back (they come super fast), while running, sent pet... <P>Fired the rest of the debufs, and sat to watch the Telamon kill the Tree! Pet gets to about 50%... some of the trees were harder and I had to nuke 3-5 times. <P>All in all, I solo'd (if you count using a pet solo) about 60 trees and 20 worms. <P>Average XP was 44-65mil/kill. Kill time was about 1minunte/tree. Down time was ZERO. <P>Sometimes I got 2 (or a tree+worm)... Use confusion to send BOTH away, because I often had to use pet to agro both to prevent me from dying (in the event of 2 trees). <P>I got continual, "Do you need help!?!?"... <P>The reply, "Nah, I'm just soloing these". <P>Just sharing this... as I've never seen anyone else solo trees :-) <P>--Cozsorc<P>--------------------<P>LvL 45 Sorcorer, Albion/Tristan<BR>LvL 41 Cleric, Albion/Tristan
