Couple of more things I've found:<P>First, you don't pull trees with a debuf-- too damn close.  You use the Lvl 8 "Wipe Agro" spell!!  The range is 2300 and the lvl 8 is NON-AOE (This is majorly important).<P>2nd, because of the range, you can pull from farther than everyone, except a Cabalist.  (Further than scouts!)<P>3rd, because trees are soo freaking resistant, even when I was lvl 49, it only took 2-3 casts to pull...<P>And-- in a a group, I'm still the designated puller.  Simply have the tanks nail the one you "agro wiped"... and the other 2+ adds will NOT come at you, making mez easssy and safe.<P>--Coz<P>--------------------<P>LvL 45 Sorcorer, Albion/Tristan<BR>LvL 41 Cleric, Albion/Tristan
